1.0.name: wordpress/cheatsheet
1.0.description: This is a quick and easy place to save tips and tricks for Wordpress administrators. After launching a new website, web designers and developers can leave notes for Wordpress administrators to reference when updating the site. The Cheatsheet link appears under the Appearance panel.
